      <title>在增长担忧触发抛售之后，亚洲股跌倒了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/asian-stocks-slump-as-global-selloff-extends-on-growth-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济增长的关注，日本令人失望的数据也使人们对情绪感到失望，因此亚洲股票下跌，遭受了第三天的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/asian-stocks-slump-as-global-selloff-extends-on-growth-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 03:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
